            <title>[LU-12981] Make a maximal transfer size check accurately. </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12981</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12140&quot; title=&quot;DOM: limitaion of data size&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12140&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12140&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; introduce a maximal transfer size check, but it make not accurately.&lt;br/&gt;
1) it have lack check for the IOV/KIOV based MD&apos;s.&lt;br/&gt;
2) It have applied to incoming buffers, but local buffers can be very large to hold a several incoming transfers.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lets fix these defects.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
